casebody.data:
Paul Craig JEFFRIES and Gerald Jeffries, as Co-Administrators of the Estate of Fanchon B. Jeffries, deceased, Plaintiffs-Appellants,
v.
CENTRAL IOWA HEALTH SYSTEM d/b/a UnityPoint Health - Des Moines and Iowa Methodist Medical Center, and Central Iowa Hospital Corp. d/b/a UnityPoint Health - Des Moines and Iowa Methodist Medical Center, Defendants-Appellees. No. 17-1897 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed January 9, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

Appeal from the grant of summary judgment in an action for breach of contract. AFFIRMED.

AFFIRMED.
